name: Doctor Delivery Cant Wait, Or can it
name_original: Doctor Delivery Cant Wait, Or can it
description: When a Doctor has no choice but to go to work, delivery might be the only option. Or is it? Being an O.B.G.Y.N is hard. It is so many distractions. Could you imaging getting stuck in traffic when a baby is on the way? OR maybe having to put a patient in the ambulance and follow the ambulance to the hospital to deliver the baby. These obstacles, choices and consequences and more.
